      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Understanding Qwen3 TTS VoiceDesign Architecture"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Qwen3 TTS VoiceDesign is a 1.7B parameter model designed for 12Hz voice output, enabling high-fidelity speech generation. It supports multiple voice styles and languages, with an API that accepts text inputs and returns audio streams. Key features include low-latency inference and customizable prosody, making it suitable for real-time applications like virtual assistants or interactive media."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Setting Up the API Environment"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "To begin, obtain an API key from the provider and ensure your environment meets the requirements: Python 3.8+ or equivalent runtime, and network access to the API endpoint. Install the official SDK via pip ("
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "pip install qwen3-tts-sdk",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": ") and configure authentication by setting the "
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "QWEN3_API_KEY",
            "code": true
          },
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": " environment variable. Test connectivity with a simple health check endpoint to verify setup before proceeding to implementation."
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "h2",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Implementing Qwen3 TTS VoiceDesign LLM API Examples"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "p",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "Integrate the API by sending POST requests to the synthesis endpoint. Below is a Python example for generating speech from text:"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "code_block",
        "lang": "python",
        "value": "import requests\nimport os\n\napi_key = os.getenv('QWEN3_API_KEY')\nendpoint = 'https://api.qwen3.ai/tts/v1/synthesize'\nheaders = {'Authorization': f'Bearer {api_key}', 'Content-Type': 'application/json'}\ndata = {\n    'text': 'Welcome to the Qwen3 TTS demonstration.',\n    'voice_id': 'en-US-neutral',\n    'speed': 1.0,\n    'format': 'mp3'\n}\n\nresponse = requests.post(endpoint, headers=headers, json=data)\nif response.status_code == 200:\n    with open('output.mp3', 'wb') as f:\n        f.write(response.content)\nelse:\n    print(f'Error: {response.status_code} - {response.text}')",
        "children": [
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "import requests"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "import os"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": ""
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "api_key = os.getenv('QWEN3_API_KEY')"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "endpoint = 'https://api.qwen3.ai/tts/v1/synthesize'"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "headers = {'Authorization': f'Bearer {api_key}', 'Content-Type': 'application/json'}"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "data = {"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "    'text': 'Welcome to the Qwen3 TTS demonstration.',"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "    'voice_id': 'en-US-neutral',"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "    'speed': 1.0,"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "    'format': 'mp3'"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "}"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": ""
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "response = requests.post(endpoint, headers=headers, json=data)"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "if response.status_code == 200:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "    with open('output.mp3', 'wb') as f:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "        f.write(response.content)"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "else:"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "code_line",
            "children": [
              {
                "text": "    print(f'Error: {response.status_code} - {response.text}')"
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
